data.description: Motivated Seller for this Beautifully updated Newport model has 2 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1 car garage.  It is located in On Top of the World, one of the most sought after 55+ communities in Ocala.   From the time pull up in the driveway, you will immediately notice the nice front porch where you can enjoy your morning coffee.  As you walk into the home,  the lovely wood look Vinyl plank floor in the living areas and both bedrooms will grab your attention.   This home is move in ready from the beautifully updated eat-in kitchen, with updated cabinets, newer hardware, newer appliances and a large pantry.  Modern pendant lighting over the bar area. There is a large Sunroom with newer wiring and great glass windows.    Master bedroom is large enough for a King Size bed and has a nice size walk-in closet.  Master bathroom has ceramic tile with a comfort height toilet.   Guest room is nice size with a newer ceiling fan.   2018 roof and HVAC. 2022 garage door opener   and springs. Hot water heater 2023.  Don't let this beautiful villa get away.  It has been very well maintained.  On Top of the World is a golf cart community.  Just a short ride to the club houses, activities, grocery store, restaurants and doctors offices.
